    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The preservation of natural or cultural resources through managed use. For example, as an ecological concept, the preservation of natural resources through responsible use and stewardship; a component of sustainable development. In context of conservation, preserving cultural heritage resources through maintenance and limited use.</Note_Text>
